Bhai maine tumhari requirement aur Stitch ke design dono compare kar liye. Abhi jo Stitch ne banaya hai usme bahut saari cheezein hain jo apne use hi nahi karenge.

### Kya rakhenge

#### Header

Ye section rakhenge:

```text
Project Name
Project Description
Domain Badge
Progress %
Team Members Count
```

Example:

```text
AI Research Agent Platform

Building AI-powered research workflows

AI / ML
68% Progress
8 Members
```

---

### Header Collapse / Slide Up

Ye tumhara sabse important requirement hai.

Default:

```text
-----------------------------------
Project Name
Description
Progress
Members
-----------------------------------
```

Jab user scroll kare ya tab switch kare:

```text
-----------------------------------
AI Research Agent Platform
68%
8 Members
-----------------------------------
```

Description hide.

Height reduce.

Sticky top header ban jayega.

Bilkul Linear / Notion style.

